{{Quote|Girls love Rominaria flowers. They smell like powdered babies.|Ian Lago|<ref name="A Summer's Dream">{{Tales|5|A Summer's Dream}}</ref>}}
The '''Rominaria flower''' was a plant native to the planet of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. It was one of the many flowers found in the [[Royal Gardens]]. The flower was a favorite to many young women, as they smelled like powdered babies.

